title: Office 2013 Home & Student x86-x64 Dutch kit
description:
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
MICROSOFT OFFICE 2013 HOME & STUDENT DUTCH X86/X64
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Contents: HomeStudentRetail.img -> Office 2013 Home & Student x86/x64 Dutch
          DTLite4491-0356 -> Daemon Tools Lite. Used for installing Office.
          Microsoft Toolkit.exe -> Used for activating Office 2013.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Step 1. Install Daemon Tools Lite.
Step 2. Open Daemon Tools Lite.
Step 3. Open image, make sure to view all file types.
Step 4. Select HomeStudentRetail.img
Step 5. Install Office, when asked for key, press X and ignore for now.
Step 6. Use Microsoft Toolkit.exe to activate your Office 2013 Home & Student installation.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Enjoy Office 2013!!
